"$ cd /Users/nelle/Desktop/data-shell\n"
"~~~"
msgstr ""

#: shell-novice/_episodes/02-filedir.md:662
msgid ""
"Run `pwd` and `ls -F` to ensure that we're in the directory we expect.  "
