"> > mv *.dat analyzed\n"
"> > ```\n"
"> > {: .language-bash}\n"
"> > Jamie needs to move her files `fructose.dat` and `sucrose.dat` to the "
"`analyzed` directory.\n"
"> > The shell will expand *.dat to match all .dat files in the current "
